# Function to auto-install and load packages
install_and_load <- function(packages) {
  for (package in packages) {
    if (!require(package, character.only = TRUE)) {
      install.packages(package, dependencies = TRUE)
      library(package, character.only = TRUE)
    }
  }
}

# List of required packages
packages <- c("dplyr", "psych", "tidyr", "GPArotation", "FactoMineR", "factoextra", "pheatmap")

# Load packages
install_and_load(packages)

# =============================================
# FACTOR ANALYSIS

# Heatmap of correlations
cor_matrix <- cor(sur_int)
pheatmap(cor_matrix, 
         main = "Correlation Heatmap",
         color = colorRampPalette(c("blue", "white", "red"))(100),
         clustering_method = "complete")

# Cluster analysis
fviz_cluster(list(data = sur_int, cluster = kmeans(sur_int, centers = 5)$cluster),
             main = "Cluster Plot")
